                    <item name="SourceCount" type_name="gh_int32" type_code="3">0</item>
                    <item name="UserText" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">"Return ONLY valid JSON.\n"
"Required output format:\n"
"{\n"
"  \"assignments\": {\"&lt;target_node_key&gt;\": \"&lt;brick_id&gt;\", ...},\n"
"  \"unassigned_targets\": [\"&lt;target_node_key&gt;\", ...],\n"
"  \"unused_bricks\": [\"&lt;brick_id&gt;\", ...],\n"
"  \"notes\": \"short\"\n"
"}\n"
"Rules (hard):\n"
"- Every target_node_key must appear exactly once in assignments OR in unassigned_targets.\n"
"- Each brick_id may appear at most once in assignments.\n"
"- If you cannot assign uniquely, put remaining targets in unassigned_targets.\n"
"- JSON only, no markdown.\n"</item>
